<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCX126378916">
<p style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: 'Segoe UI',Tahoma,Verdana,'Sans-Serif'; background-color: transparent; color: windowtext; text-align: justify; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; text-indent: 14px; font-size: 6pt;" class="Paragraph SCX126378916"><span class="TextRun SCX126378916" style="color: #202020; background-color: #f4f4f4; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; line-height: 29px;" lang="ES-ES"><span style="background-color: inherit;" class="NormalTextRun SCX126378916">Base imponible= 208.000 €.</span></span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 29px; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif;" class="EOP SCX126378916"> </span></p>
